----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage:
./caltran -mode "expression" #The " " are important for functions with ( )
	-mode:
		-r	#Uses real numbers
		-c	#Uses complex numbers
			#Format of complex numbers: (real.decimal,complex.decimal)
			#Exemple: ./caltran -c "sqrt(-1.0,0.0)"
		-h	#Print this help
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
